react-native-config


react-native-fbsdk:
Make sure you have the latest Xcode installed. Open the .xcodeproj in Xcode found in the ios subfolder from your project's root directory. 
Now, follow all the steps except the pod install (Step 2) in the Getting Started Guide (https://developers.facebook.com/docs/ios/getting-started/) for Facebook SDK for iOS. 
Along with FBSDKCoreKit.framework, don't forget to import FBSDKShareKit.framework and FBSDKLoginKit.framework into your Xcode project.


